Architecture plan for `miketang84-forum001`

Project shape
- Plain Rust web app using Axum, SQLx, Askama, tower-sessions, Tailwind, and PostgreSQL.
- Single binary crate with server-rendered HTML pages and static assets.
- Keep the initial issue scope oriented around a monolith with strong module boundaries so later extraction is optional rather than required.

